# Technology Stack

Develop a cross-platform, intuitive frontend using React Native, ensuring seamless performance in a browser and on both iOS and Android devices.

Utilize a user-friendly Python framework (FastAPI) for backend development to ensure rapid development and maintainability.

The dev version has to be deployed locally and test with prod versions will be deployed on Google Cloud Platform (GCP).

Store user notes securely and efficiently by using secure database solutions (Postgres SQL).

Implement easy and secure user authentication, for example, through Google Sign-In.

Leverage a robust existing AI model such as Google Cloud's Speech-to-Text API (https://cloud.google.com/speech-to-text/docs/reference/rest/v1/operations) for accurate voice-to-text transcription.

Use version control with Git.